Reasoning: The paper proposes methods for encoding and learning linear dynamical systems, which are commonly used in time-series analysis and video processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves optimization and sparse coding, which are relevant to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.SD (Systems and Control).
